GymCo
├─ Overview
│   └─ A mobile app designed for gym-goers to plan, start, and track their workouts, discover training routines, explore gym events, and monitor their personal fitness journey.
│
├─ User Persona
│   └─ Member A – self-motivated gym-goer who wants to follow structured workouts, track progress, and explore events or training opportunities at their gym.
│
├─ Core Modules
│   ├─ Authentication
│   │   ├─ Email/password or phone OTP login
│   │   └─ Social login optional
│
│   ├─ Dashboard
│   │   ├─ Personalized greeting and today’s plan
│   │   ├─ Current streaks or progress highlights
│   │   └─ Quick access to start workout or log activity
│
│   ├─ Workout Planner
│   │   ├─ Create daily workout to-do list
│   │   ├─ Select from presets or add custom sets/reps
│   │   └─ Save as template for reuse
│
│   ├─ Workout Timer
│   │   ├─ Start a workout session (Pomodoro-style or free mode)
│   │   ├─ Track total duration and rest intervals
│   │   └─ Pause, skip, or end workout
│
│   ├─ Explore
│   │   ├─ Discover workout routines by goal (strength, fat burn, etc.)
│   │   ├─ Filter by time, difficulty, or equipment
│   │   └─ Save routines to personal planner
│
│   ├─ Events and Training
│   │   ├─ View upcoming gym events or group challenges
│   │   ├─ Register for workshops or bootcamps
│   │   └─ Book personal training or assessment slots
│
│   ├─ Log
│   │   ├─ Track finished workouts by date
│   │   ├─ View progress: streaks, calories, time spent
│   │   └─ Export logs or share with a trainer
│
│   └─ Profile
│       ├─ Edit personal goals and preferences
│       ├─ View account/membership info
│       └─ Connect wearables or health app data
│
├─ Tabs
├─ Home
│   ├─ Daily Overview
│   │   ├─ Display current day’s planned workout or rest day
│   │   ├─ Quick action to start, resume, or log workout
│   │   └─ Smart rest day suggestions based on fatigue or streak
│   │
│   ├─ Progress Dashboard
│   │   ├─ Weekly and monthly workout streak tracker
│   │   ├─ Time spent in zones (strength, cardio, recovery)
│   │   └─ Personal records and badges earned
│   │
│   ├─ Health Sync (optional)
│   │   ├─ Show heart rate, calories, and steps (sync with wearables)
│   │   └─ Recovery status or readiness score
│   │
│   └─ Smart Suggestions
│       ├─ Recommended plan based on past logs
│       ├─ Suggested routines based on time of day and energy level
│       └─ Motivational quote or video

│
├─ Plan
│   ├─ Workout Builder
│   │   ├─ Build routines using preset exercises or custom inputs
│   │   ├─ Drag and drop sets, reps, rest intervals
│   │   └─ Add supersets, drop sets, warm-ups and cooldowns
│   │
│   ├─ Workout Scheduler
│   │   ├─ Plan weekly/monthly schedule (auto recommend gaps)
│   │   └─ Sync with personal calendar or reminders
│   │
│   ├─ Active Session
│   │   ├─ In-session tracker with timer, sound cues, swipe navigation
│   │   ├─ Real-time progress bar and next exercise preview
│   │   └─ Rest countdown with optional music or breathing guide
│   │
│   └─ Post Workout Summary
│       ├─ Input RPE (rate of perceived exertion), notes, injury flag
│       ├─ Calories burned, estimated volume lifted
│       └─ Option to save session as template

│
├─ Explore
│   ├─ Workout Library
│   │   ├─ Filter routines by goals (fat loss, hypertrophy, strength)
│   │   ├─ Categories: No-equipment, Dumbbell-only, Gym machines
│   │   └─ Browse by duration, body focus, or level
│   │
│   ├─ Video Tutorials
│   │   ├─ High-quality video walkthroughs of each exercise
│   │   ├─ Tips for form correction and common mistakes
│   │   └─ Option to bookmark or queue for offline viewing
│   │
│   ├─ Community Picks
│   │   ├─ See top routines liked by others in your gym or area
│   │   └─ Comment, like, and save to plan
│   │
│   └─ AI Recommendations
│       ├─ Suggest full routine based on past progress or skipped days
│       ├─ Dynamic adjuster if you say “I have 30 mins and 2 dumbbells”
│       └─ Weekly challenges (e.g., "Leg Burner of the Week")

│
├─ Profile
│   ├─ Personal Dashboard
│   │   ├─ View and edit name, weight, height, fitness goals
│   │   └─ Adjust training difficulty or focus
│   │
│   ├─ Progress Tracker
│   │   ├─ Timeline of body stats, strength gains, and logged sessions
│   │   └─ Export progress to PDF or share to coach
│   │
│   ├─ Preferences and Settings
│   │   ├─ Toggle dark mode, units (lbs/kg), rest timer duration
│   │   └─ Connect devices (Apple Health, Google Fit, Garmin, etc.)
│   │
│   └─ Help and Support
│       ├─ FAQs and app tutorials
│       ├─ Chat or contact trainer/instructor
│       └─ App feedback and bug report

│
├─ Stretch Ideas
│   ├─ Real-time heart rate integration (via wearable)
│   ├─ AI-generated workout plan from past log history
│   ├─ Challenge friends or unlock achievement badges
│   └─ Monthly report card summarizing effort and improvements
